claims:
1.一种电极组件，其特征在于，包括叠加设置的正极极片和负极极片；1. An electrode assembly, characterized in that it comprises a positive electrode sheet and a negative electrode sheet stacked together;


         所述正极极片包括正极集流体和正极活性物质层，所述正极集流体包括正极涂覆区和正极极耳，所述正极活性物质层至少部分涂覆于所述正极涂覆区，所述正极极耳连接于所述正极涂覆区沿第一方向的端部，所述第一方向垂直于所述正极极片和所述负极极片的叠加方向；The positive electrode sheet comprises a positive electrode current collector and a positive electrode active material layer, the positive electrode current collector comprises a positive electrode coating area and a positive electrode tab, the positive electrode active material layer is at least partially coated on the positive electrode coating area, and the positive electrode tab is connected to an end of the positive electrode coating area along a first direction, and the first direction is perpendicular to the stacking direction of the positive electrode sheet and the negative electrode sheet;


         所述正极活性物质层与所述负极极片的负极活性物质层面对设置，并且所述负极活性物质层的端部超出所述正极活性物质层；The positive electrode active material layer is arranged opposite to the negative electrode active material layer of the negative electrode plate, and the end of the negative electrode active material layer exceeds the positive electrode active material layer;


         所述正极活性物质层包括正极主体部和连接于所述正极主体部的正极边缘部，所述正极边缘部被配置为：所述正极边缘部的单位面积容量小于所述正极主体部的单位面积容量；The positive electrode active material layer includes a positive electrode main body and a positive electrode edge portion connected to the positive electrode main body, wherein the positive electrode edge portion is configured such that: the capacity per unit area of the positive electrode edge portion is smaller than the capacity per unit area of the positive electrode main body;


         所述正极边缘部至少为两个，两个所述正极边缘部分别位于所述正极主体部沿所述第一方向的两侧。There are at least two positive electrode edge portions, and the two positive electrode edge portions are respectively located on two sides of the positive electrode main body portion along the first direction.

5.根据权利要求2所述的电极组件，其特征在于，5. The electrode assembly according to claim 2, characterized in that:


         所述负极边缘部包括沿所述叠加方向层叠设置的第一负极涂层和第二负极涂层；The negative electrode edge portion includes a first negative electrode coating and a second negative electrode coating stacked along the stacking direction;


         所述第二负极涂层中的活性材料与所述第二负极涂层的重量比大于所述第一负极涂层中的活性材料与所述第一负极涂层的重量比；或者，所述第二负极涂层中的活性材料的克容量大于所述第一负极涂层中的活性材料的克容量。The weight ratio of the active material in the second negative electrode coating to the second negative electrode coating is greater than the weight ratio of the active material in the first negative electrode coating to the first negative electrode coating; or, the gram capacity of the active material in the second negative electrode coating is greater than the gram capacity of the active material in the first negative electrode coating.

7.根据权利要求2所述的电极组件，其特征在于，7. The electrode assembly according to claim 2, characterized in that:


         所述负极极片包括负极集流体，所述负极集流体包括负极涂覆区和负极极耳，所述负极活性物质层至少部分涂覆于所述负极涂覆区，所述负极极耳连接于所述负极涂覆区沿所述第一方向的端部；The negative electrode sheet includes a negative electrode current collector, the negative electrode current collector includes a negative electrode coating area and a negative electrode tab, the negative electrode active material layer is at least partially coated on the negative electrode coating area, and the negative electrode tab is connected to an end of the negative electrode coating area along the first direction;


         所述负极边缘部至少为两个，两个所述负极边缘部分别位于所述负极主体部沿所述第一方向的两侧。There are at least two negative electrode edge portions, and the two negative electrode edge portions are respectively located on two sides of the negative electrode main body portion along the first direction.

14.根据权利要求1所述的电极组件，其特征在于，14. The electrode assembly according to claim 1, characterized in that:


         所述正极边缘部包括沿所述叠加方向层叠设置的第一正极涂层和第二正极涂层；The positive electrode edge portion includes a first positive electrode coating and a second positive electrode coating stacked along the stacking direction;


         所述第二正极涂层中的活性材料与所述第二正极涂层的重量比小于所述第一正极涂层中的活性材料与所述第一正极涂层的重量比；或者，所述第二正极涂层中的活性材料的克容量小于所述第一正极涂层中的活性材料的克容量。The weight ratio of the active material in the second positive electrode coating to the second positive electrode coating is less than the weight ratio of the active material in the first positive electrode coating to the first positive electrode coating; or, the gram capacity of the active material in the second positive electrode coating is less than the gram capacity of the active material in the first positive electrode coating.

